00:19:30.900 --> 00:19:32.099
Apakah kamu menemukan sesuatu?

00:19:34.081 --> 00:19:36.779
Nenek, aku tahu
segalanya tentang Kavita.

00:19:36.859 --> 00:19:38.295
Dia alergi kacang.

00:19:38.375 --> 00:19:40.668
